Implemented `log_frontend_filter_get` at line 594. The function delegates to the existing `filter_get` with `LOG_FRONTEND_SLOT_ID` and `Z_LOG_LOCAL_DOMAIN_ID`, mirroring the pattern of `z_impl_log_frontend_filter_set` and `log_filter_get`:

- `filter_get` handles the runtime vs compiled level logic based on the `runtime` parameter
- `LOG_FRONTEND_SLOT_ID` identifies the frontend's slot (same as the setter)
- `Z_LOG_LOCAL_DOMAIN_ID` restricts it to the local domain (frontend is always local)


